## How to Run
1. Open the .Rmd file in RStudio  
2. Install required packages (listed at the top of the file)  
3. Knit to HTML to generate the full report  

## Summary
This project represents a complete sports analytics workflow: importing data, engineering new features, constructing performance metrics, visualizing trends, and producing a cohesive analytical report. It reflects techniques regularly used in NBA front offices and applied sports-science environments.
